{"id":96789,"type":6,"name":"24: Live Another Day","name_cn":"24小时：再活一天","date":"2014-05-05","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/d0/db/96789_zVJYn.jpg","rating":{"rank":1291,"total":23,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":3,"5":2,"6":0,"7":6,"8":9,"9":1,"10":2},"score":7.2},"summary":"　　2013年5月13日，FOX电视台正式宣布，《24小时》的新故事将以迷你剧形式将在2014年回归，名称正式确定为《24小时：再活一天》。在《24小时》宣告完结之后，电视剧主创和主演基弗·萨瑟兰一直在尝试着去拍摄《24小时》的电影版，不过计划一直未被落实。此次，萨瑟兰将在续作中继续饰演“不死特工”杰克·鲍尔，不过剧集的长度将从之前的24集缩短为12集。 \r\n　　《再活一天》的故事将发生在第八季结束后几年，依然以一天时间为范围，每一集讲述在一个小时内发生的事情，但不再进行连续性叙述，下一集可能会跳跃到几小时后。除萨瑟兰以外，其他主演和具体剧情均未确定。有消息称，FOX电视台已邀请历代《24小时》的演员回归。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>24小时：再活一天</li><li><span>主演: </span><a href=\"/person/33108\">Yvonne Strahovski</a>、<a href=\"/person/25068\">Kiefer Sutherland</a>、<a href=\"/person/29067\">Michelle Fairley</a>、<a href=\"/person/33472\">Stephen Fry</a></li><li><span>配角: </span><a href=\"/person/47344\">Miranda Raison</a></li><li><span>集数: </span>12</li><li><span>开始: </span>2014-05-05</li><li><span>类型: </span>剧情 / 动作 / 犯罪</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>美国</li><li><span>语言: </span>英语</li><li><span>电视台: </span>FOX</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>http://www.fox.com/24-live-another-day/</li><li><span>imdb_id: </span>tt1598754</li><li><span>wiki: </span>http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/24:_Live_Another_Day</li>","collection":{"on_hold":1,"dropped":1,"wish":11,"collect":33,"doing":2},"tags":[{"name":"美剧","count":16},{"name":"2014","count":3},{"name":"Fox","count":2},{"name":"剧集","count":1},{"name":"明珠台","count":1},{"name":"动作","count":1},{"name":"TV","count":1},{"name":"剧情","count":1},{"name":"","count":""}],"eps":[{"id":372245,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/372245","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"Day 9: 11:00 a.m. – 12:00 p.m.","duration":"","airdate":"2014-05-04","comment":1,"desc":""},{"id":372246,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/372246","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"Day 9: 12:00 p.m. – 1:00 p.m.","duration":"","airdate":"2014-05-04","comment":0,"desc":""},{"id":372247,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/372247","type":0,"sort":3,"name":